title: DJ Khaled – “Shining” (Feat. Beyoncé & Jay Z) - Stereogum
text:
James Rettig @jmret | February 12, 2017 - 11:47 pm Share < br />this article: 
Right as the Grammys were wrapping up (and Adele was accepting the awards for Best Record and Best Album Of The Year), DJ Khaled released a new track called “Shining” that features none other than Beyoncé and Jay Z. (Have you heard of them?) Right now, it’s a TIDAL exclusive, but if you happen to have that, you can listen to it below.
